sequenceDiagram
    participant App as bootstrap()
    participant SS as ServerSupervisor
    participant BP as createBrowserPane()
    App->>SS: new ServerSupervisor({repoRoot, project, session, cdpPort})
    App->>SS: supervisor.start()
    SS-->>App: {port, attached}
    App->>BP: createBrowserPane(mainWindow, {0,0,0,0})
    BP-->>App: browserPane (BrowserPane)
    Note over App: No control server<br/>No paneManager IPC<br/>No env injection for control URL/token
